sinne: your deuotion is blinde, and not godly, but like her mother Ignorance: you are disobedient to Christian Magistrates, submitting your selues to Antichrist: your grauitie and constancie in all cases, is better commended of your self, then knowne of other men: Wherefore being voyde euen of these, which you make the signes of the true Church, you are none of the true Church, except you recant.
