                      and certeine sentences alleaged out of them, by most auncient doctors and councells. VVith whome, the aduersaries if they list be busie, shall wrestle, for I will seeke out as my purpose was, whether in other times and vsages of celebration, this kinde memoriall of the deade, hath not bene kept.
               
