namely and before all other, for the Byshoppes resting in this place. And then he prayeth thus: Remembre Lorde and haue mercy, and shewe thy fauourable grace to all the soules deceased, pacifie and illuminate them, adioyne them to the company of holy sainctes in heauen, and make them worthy of thy loue.
                  
               
